      <a href="/mushroom/" class="ac">
        <span class="ac-tag">Mushrooms & Adaptogens</span>
        <h3>Mushroom Gummies Hub</h3>
        <p>Lion's mane, ashwagandha, and mushroom blend gummies for cognitive function and stress management.</p>
        <span class="ac-btn">Explore Mushrooms →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/trending/" class="ac">
